The '''Escuela Superior de Guerra''' (founded 1909) is a military college under the [[Military Forces of Colombia]]. It was founded during the reforms of President [[Rafael Reyes]], himself a former general.<ref>Historical Dictionary of Colombia Harvey F. Kline - 2012 "ESCUELA SUPERIOR DE GUERRA. The institution of higher education of the armed forces. It was founded in 1909 at the time of the military reform of President Rafael Reyes, a former general, in the spirit of professionalization of military ..."</ref> Alumni include President [[Gabriel París Gordillo]].

